➜汪太银好人歌
http://www.sohu.com/a/258125890_528362	6216
<p class="ql-align-justify">太银命笔是上班，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">天天忙碌公益圈。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不比吃来不追穿，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不求有钱不求官。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不求房来小单间，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">东奔西跑日月年。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">奇山异景大边关，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">全国各地文化传。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181008/d78f9be5ae2b4fd9b2599f5b5866779c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181008/c55a689c25824f679f87d98b57e17691.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181008/dce7383498da4fce93c18a635722d9a0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">唱歌吟诗撒个欢，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一路坎坷也平坦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">碰见熟人打个扦，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">品茶论道正义担。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">遇事不钻牛角尖，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">马路草坪睡休闲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大千世界万事现，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">永远跟党好路线。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">文化记载好人事，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">金钱地位是云烟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">笔墨纸印常配伴，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">心里常驻艳阳天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">伯虎羲之烟云过，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">太银好人在中原。</p>